---
Source:
  - Title: Treasury of Traditional Wisdom
    Page: 344
Tags:
  - Combat-Action=Work, Action and Society=God the Only Doer
By: \'Ali
---
Whoever is the object of divine beneficence will be solicited on all
sides. If he dispenses his gifts according to the will of heaven, his
happiness will be lasting; if not, it will be ephemeral.
